    "template": "content",
    "texts": [
     "{\"template\":\"intro\",\"texts\":[\"Certain manoeuvres (turns) are banned on some of our roads. Ignoring these bans can be very dangerous and could result in an accident.\"],\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"image\",\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{\"url\":\"https://tfl.gov.uk/ruc-cdn/static/cms/images/no-right.jpg\"},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "A banned manoeuvre occurs when drivers ignore signs giving\n        instructions as to a direction they must\n        or must not take.",
     "The signs are located\n        before\n        the banned manoeuvre and often additional signage will provide an advanced\n        warning.",
     "Enforcement of banned manoeuvres helps to manage how traffic uses the road and makes it safer for pedestrians.",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"Recognising a banned manoeuvre sign\"}",
     "These signs are listed in the Highway Code and\n        are not unique to the red route. They are either signs with:",
     "{\"template\":\"bulletlist\",\"items\":[\"A white arrow on a blue background showing you\\n            the direction you must take, or\",\"A red outer circle showing you the direction you must not take\"]}",
     "When using the Transport for London Road\n        Network (TLRN), known as 'red routes', you will see signs with a white arrow\n        on a blue background, which have the following meaning:",
     "{\"template\":\"image\",\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{\"url\":\"https://tfl.gov.uk/ruc-cdn/static/cms/images/blue-straight-ahead.jpg\"},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h4\",\"value\":\"Straight ahead only\"}",
     "You must continue ahead only.",
     "You must not turn left, right or make a U turn.",
     "{\"template\":\"image\",\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{\"url\":\"https://tfl.gov.uk/ruc-cdn/static/cms/images/blue-left-ahead.jpg\"},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h4\",\"value\":\"Left turn ahead\"}",
     "You must turn left at the junction ahead.",
     "{\"template\":\"image\",\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{\"url\":\"https://tfl.gov.uk/ruc-cdn/static/cms/images/blue-right-ahead.jpg\"},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h4\",\"value\":\"Right turn ahead\"}",
     "You must turn right at the junction ahead.",
     "You must not turn left, go straight ahead or make a U turn.",
     "{\"template\":\"image\",\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{\"url\":\"https://tfl.gov.uk/ruc-cdn/static/cms/images/blue-left.jpg\"},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h4\",\"value\":\"Turn left\"}",
     "You must turn left.",
     "{\"template\":\"image\",\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{\"url\":\"https://tfl.gov.uk/ruc-cdn/static/cms/images/blue-right.jpg\"},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h4\",\"value\":\"Right turn\"}",
     "You must turn right.",
     "You must not turn left, go straight ahead or make a U turn.",
     "When using the red route you\n        will see signs with a red outer circle, they have the following meaning:",
     "{\"template\":\"image\",\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{\"url\":\"https://tfl.gov.uk/ruc-cdn/static/cms/images/no-right-turn.jpg\"},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h4\",\"value\":\"Can do\"}",
     "Go ahead or make a left hand turn.",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h4\",\"value\":\"Can't do\"}",
     "Turn right.",
     "{\"template\":\"image\",\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{\"url\":\"https://tfl.gov.uk/ruc-cdn/static/cms/images/no-left-turn.jpg\"},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h4\",\"value\":\"Can do\"}",
     "Turn right or straight ahead.",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h4\",\"value\":\"Can't do\"}",
     "Turn left.",
     "{\"template\":\"image\",\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{\"url\":\"https://tfl.gov.uk/ruc-cdn/static/cms/images/no-u-turn.jpg\"},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h4\",\"value\":\"Can do\"}",
     "Drive ahead or make a left or right turn.",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h4\",\"value\":\"Can't do\"}",
     "Make a U-turn.",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"Penalty Charge Notices (PCNs)\"}",
     "We issue PCNs to deter\n        drivers from breaking the rules and endangering other road users.",
     " \u003ca href=\"/modes/driving/red-routes/penalty-charge-notices\"\u003eFind out more about Penalty Charge Notices\u003c/a\u003e ."
    ],
